<div class="page-flexbox-wrapper">
  <div id="event-header">
    <h1>Mission Trail</h1>
    <br>
  </div>
    <div id="top-content-buffer"></div>
      <div class="welcome-container">
        <p>Your mission, should you choose to accept it: <br>
        <p>A hip, new, trendy bar has just opened in the Marina District. Due to ethical concerns, all ride-sharing services have been banned. You have to make it to this party before your FOMO increases and you literally can't even.</p> 
        <p> Traveling by foot, you have one hour to make it to the Marina. You are about to witness the struggle of the modern Millenial... </p>
        <p>The struggle is real.</p>
      </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <%= audio_tag("INTRO.mp3", autoplay: true) %>
    <div class="all-options">
      <div class="options">
        <%= link_to "Start Game", { :action => "show"}, :method => :get %>
        <br>
         <%= link_to "Leaderboard", scoreboard_index_path%>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
